{"tid":2027134,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"共產黨打到嚟喇","createTime":"2020-05-21T10:04:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T10:21:15.000Z","uid":1354,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bffa42d47a1e3008b8f5436220cfd5bf37098db5","tid":2027134,"uid":1354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:04:58.000Z","msg":"睇到個標題嚇到叫左出黎，老細問咩事，我照讀比佢聽，讀左標題內文都未開始讀，佢成塊面白哂，自言自語，猛咁話「共慘黨殺到黎，香港九龍新界無得避，要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生；共慘黨殺到黎，香港九龍新界無得避，要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n跟住衝左上天台，叫左一聲「鳴呀，點解係我」就跳左落去，成班同事追上去都追唔切，有兩個女同事嚇到暈左，仲有個男同事當場嚇到變左弱智，不停問人要唔要食腸仔蛋。<br />\n<br />\n我就好好彩無咩事，但同班同事五十幾個人即時變左失業，你條仆街真係害人害物&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"90defcf020aeb0f584d28114d8238aabfd1d2040","tid":2027134,"uid":1354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:08:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"091814c1cf782f00e59e3c01b91bc818be870ccd","tid":2027134,"uid":42340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:12:46.000Z","msg":"電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmo